cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE. 

The paper deals with medical image segmentation and classification using deep learning and handcrafted features. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The use of deep learning models for segmentation and classification also suggests the possibility of the paper belonging to cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Additionally, the use of medical imaging data suggests the possibility of the paper belonging to cs.MM (Multimedia).
